snippet.title: Monadic Media
snippet.description:
The purpose of this channel is to present the ageless wisdom through the medium of multimedia; while utilizing the methods of color and sound to help awaken the intuition. 

For future content consider supporting our Patreon: www.patreon.com/MonadicMedia

Want to connect with our community? Join our FB Page: https://www.facebook.com/Monadic-Media-107723213977169/
